graph TD
    Upload[TXT File Upload] --> Validate{Security Validation}
    Validate -->|.txt only| SizeCheck[Size Limit Check]
    Validate -->|blocked| Reject[Reject Non-TXT]
    SizeCheck --> Write[Stream Write to Disk<br>Random Filename]
    Write --> Detect[Multi-Encoding Detection<br>UTF-8 / GB18030 / Big5 / Shift_JIS]
    Detect --> Clean[Text Cleaning<br>BOM / Whitespace / Newlines]
    Clean --> Split[Chapter Splitting<br>Regex: 第X章 / Chapter X]
    Split --> Txn[Database Transaction]
    
    subgraph "Transaction"
        Txn --> InsertNovel[INSERT Novel]
        InsertNovel --> InsertChapters[INSERT Chapters Batch]
        InsertChapters --> InsertJob[INSERT ImportJob]
    end
    
    InsertJob -->|success| Done[Return Import Result]
    InsertJob -->|failure| Compensate[Delete Uploaded File<br>Rollback Transaction]
    
    Done --> Index[Trigger RAG Indexing<br>optional]

    style Validate fill:#ffebee
    style Reject fill:#ffcdd2
    style Txn fill:#e8f5e9
    style Done fill:#c8e6c9
    style Compensate fill:#ffcdd2
